description: Welcome to 1 Leonard Place. This 2 bed 2 bath home is located on the East Side of South Boston nestled on a quaint dead end street. Newly built in 2018, this home is young and in impeccable shape. The kitchen features custom cabinetry, Subzero double door fridge, Wolf oven/stove top, oversized island with butcher block top and tons of cabinet space. The open layout is designed perfectly with designated dining & living space finished with multiple large windows. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom with glass enclosed walk in-shower and large walk-in closet. Just across the hall you will find a spacious second bedroom and bathroom. Condo is finished with central air, in unit washer dryer, garage parking and Juke Audio multi- room sound system. Moments to some of the best dining spots in Boston, multiple bus lines and gorgeous Medal of Honor Park. Easy to Show.
